        "content": "<p>\"While most puns<br>\n  make me numb<br>\n  math puns make me <br>\n  feel number\"</p>\n<p>You can posts your thoughts on this <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bsletten/status/1350562889979990016\">here</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"inline-preview-twitter\"><div class=\"twitter-tweet\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/bsletten/status/1350562889979990016\"><img class=\"twitter-avatar\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1129462689892225024/6otA3cso_normal.jpg\"></a><p>Don’t know the origin but I knew you needed this... <a href=\"https://t.co/jw6RYKSh3L\">https://twitter.com/bsletten/status/1350562889979990016/photo/1</a></p><span>- bsletten (@bsletten)</span><div class=\"twitter-image\"><a href=\"https://t.co/jw6RYKSh3L\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Er4pymzVEAARjYJ.jpg:thumb\"></a></div></div></div>",
